# Prettier ignore — intent-eval-lab
#
# Machine-generated eval-result files under research/*/results/** are not
# authored prose; formatting them produces noise and renders the advisory
# prettier-md gate permanently red. Exclude every baseline's results dir so
# the gate carries real signal on authored docs only.
#
# NOTE: the doc-quality.yml prettier step passes BOTH --ignore-path .gitignore
# AND --ignore-path .prettierignore (prettier 3.x honors multiple ignore
# paths). A bare .prettierignore is NOT auto-read when --ignore-path is set
# explicitly, so the workflow flag is load-bearing.
research/**/results/**
